Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.00,0:00:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.64,0:00:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.54,0:00:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.38,0:00:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people\Nseek the answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.48,0:00:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future --\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.54,0:00:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright,\Nbut I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.54,0:00:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.15,0:00:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.55,0:01:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.99,0:01:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.33,0:01:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.14,0:01:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.44,0:01:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.58,0:01:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really\Nneed everything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.59,0:01:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.76,0:01:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.36,0:01:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.14,0:02:04.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Yuba" "Erumalu" "Nanohana" "Katorea"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.47,0:01:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three years have passed since\Na single drop of rain fell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.91,0:02:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the kingdom of oases.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.05,0:02:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The burning land is now\Nenveloped by a mighty swell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.75,0:02:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After parting with Ace, Luffy\Nand company continue to trek
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.49,0:02:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,through the vast desert\Nas they hurry to Yuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.39,0:02:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for whether they can stop\Nthe beleaguered rebel army...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the setting sun watches\Nover them silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ruins and Lost Ways!\NVivi, Her Friends, and the Country's Form"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.76,0:02:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he's back with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.03,0:02:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you finally sane again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.23,0:02:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.84,0:03:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wha? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.17,0:03:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Where are the others?\N--Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm not sure, to be more precise.\N--Don't be funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.05,0:03:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--This is no time to be laughing!\N--Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.78,0:03:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we're lost again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.05,0:03:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose fault do you think that is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.39,0:03:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha? M-My fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.80,0:03:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Get back here, Crocodile!\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What's he freaking out about?\N--I'm gonna kick your butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.34,0:03:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus he's flying...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he eat another weird cactus?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.34,0:03:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh! Can't he ever not cause trouble?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.18,0:03:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.68,0:03:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think he can help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.32,0:03:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, geez. Alright, Zoro. It's up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Why me?!\N--Want me to talk more about your debt?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.53,0:03:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't end up in hell,\NI'm gonna kick you down there myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:04:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.23,0:04:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.63,0:04:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Shouldn't we wait for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.57,0:04:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can just follow our footprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.17,0:04:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With their strength,\Nthey'll catch up in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can wait somewhere relaxing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.38,0:04:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agreed...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.41,0:04:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will they really be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.68,0:04:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.52,0:04:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Urgh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stick him with a needle\Nor something, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O...kay...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.76,0:04:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't count on anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crocodile!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.48,0:04:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.95,0:04:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You dumbass! Don't make me...\N--...kick your butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...wake you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.48,0:04:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Submarine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though this happens\Nevery single time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.56,0:05:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...stopping him when\Nhe's gone crazy is a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.26,0:05:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Urgh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.81,0:05:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did I wind up\Nfollowing a captain like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.61,0:05:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww! Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.31,0:05:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.62,0:06:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.05,0:06:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!\NWhat in the world happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.82,0:06:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Zoro! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.19,0:06:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.63,0:06:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A restorative!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.23,0:06:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What were you doing?!\N--Stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.90,0:06:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still buried.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.51,0:06:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave him be for now.\NWhere are the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.98,0:06:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were gone when I came to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.68,0:06:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those coldhearted bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's alright. We can\Njust follow their footprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.02,0:06:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, footprints?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.02,0:06:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're actually Crocodile?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.86,0:06:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.99,0:06:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? We got separated?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't we go after them sooner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper! You smell things good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.94,0:06:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already trying. But\NI don't smell anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.54,0:06:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we have no clues at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.51,0:06:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which way is the wind blowing from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the direction,\Nbut it's coming from our left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.28,0:07:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Left, huh? That at least\Nmeans they didn't go that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.55,0:07:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just makin' that up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.05,0:07:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Stay here if that's\Nwhat you want! Let's go, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.96,0:07:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, wait for me!\NDon't leave me behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.93,0:07:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.90,0:07:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will be he all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.97,0:07:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not the kind to\Nkick the bucket so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.57,0:07:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Say.\N--Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.24,0:07:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is pirate life always like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.41,0:07:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.65,0:07:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always climbing snowy\Nmountains, crossing deserts...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't that the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we're just a little out of the\Nordinary. Plus there's our captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I might've gotten on\Nboard a not-so-good ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a coincidence. I was just\Nthinking the same thing myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.33,0:07:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Say.\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.33,0:07:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the most veteran\Ncrew member here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:08:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess, but there's not that\Nmuch of a difference between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.27,0:08:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you join?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To me, since I just joined,\Nit seems like everyone's a maverick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.85,0:08:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true. In my case, things\Npretty much just turned out this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The others are the same.\NOur real goals are different from his.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.76,0:08:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're trying to do what we want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.83,0:08:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's crazy. It's just like\Nsomeone said before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the outside,\Nwe have no teamwork at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.81,0:08:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially given our captain.\NHe's a real handful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.51,0:08:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.81,0:08:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, really, what is teamwork?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is helping each other and\Nprotecting each other enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.69,0:08:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some people say so,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but, sorry, that only sounds\Nlike they're fooling themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.90,0:08:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think teamwork only begins
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.33,0:09:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when everyone risks their lives\Nto do what they can and then says,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I did it! You're up next!\NIf you can't do it, I'll kill you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.14,0:09:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you think about it that way,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what's wrong with having\Nmavericks as companions?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.08,0:09:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my opinion, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.15,0:09:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what Usopp meant by,\N"Just do what you can!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.42,0:09:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like BS\Nwhen he says it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.09,0:09:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for why I still stay with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.76,0:09:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...being by his side all this time's\Ngiven me another goal to strive for.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.07,0:09:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.77,0:09:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I dunno how to answer about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.01,0:09:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found shade!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.56,0:10:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice and cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.43,0:10:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I oughta chop you apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! My bad! My bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.77,0:10:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's Chopper?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.60,0:10:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he doing out there?\NIs he trying to act funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.44,0:10:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It was my fault. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.88,0:10:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez! What was the point\Nof that conversation--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.88,0:10:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. I didn't know\Nyou were a comedian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.12,0:10:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.82,0:10:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You're okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.22,0:10:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.96,0:10:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.12,0:11:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.43,0:11:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's something like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.50,0:11:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...doing underground?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.03,0:11:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you down here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.83,0:11:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I used my arms.\N--I'm asking why!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.20,0:11:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Just 'cause.\N--You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.80,0:11:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With you down here too, we might\Nget separated from Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without him, we'll never meet\Nup with Vivi and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.44,0:11:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh! That's okay!\N--Why is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.11,0:11:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Chopper was\Nfalling down here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.65,0:11:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.06,0:11:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.96,0:11:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heya. You seem to be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro! Luffy! Where is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.26,0:11:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No idea. But whatever it is,\Nit's definitely underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.10,0:11:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Underground?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.47,0:11:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm exhausted!\NLet's take a short break!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.71,0:11:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.04,0:12:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon! You're pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.31,0:12:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy for you to say! You rode Lashes!\NWe gotta walk the whole way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.22,0:12:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Lashes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.85,0:12:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.09,0:12:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will Luffy-san and the\Nothers know where to find us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.79,0:12:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think they'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're on top of a hill. It stood\Nout clearly, even from far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.76,0:12:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.20,0:12:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say. How much further to Yuba?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.37,0:12:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing as we made it to these ruins,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.50,0:12:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we should be there by night\Nif we continue walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.11,0:12:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Close, at last...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.88,0:12:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? So these are ruins?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I believe they're\Nfrom quite an old era.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Civilizations first began\Nhere thousands of years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.35,0:12:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Many kingdoms have risen and fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.36,0:12:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Resettlement in search of water,\Nthe occasional war...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.43,0:12:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruins of such things remain\Nall throughout this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.13,0:12:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Many are full of mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:13:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And time flowed on, leading to\Nthe Alabasta dynasty of today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an epic story. A prosperous\Nkingdom, destined to disappear...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.08,0:13:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.98,0:13:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Vivi-chan!\NI didn't mean it like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.92,0:13:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just, you know, a figure of speech...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.72,0:13:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.29,0:13:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've often felt the same way as of late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what is a country?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.60,0:13:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the ruler of a land changes,\Nits people will keep on living.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.43,0:13:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Culture, lifestyle...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If those stay the same even\Nwhen a country changes,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.01,0:13:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's really necessary\Nto struggle to protect the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.68,0:13:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly, there are other\Nthings that need protecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.68,0:13:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since the sand pirates and the\Ntown with the fake rebel soldiers,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.75,0:13:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking that way a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! That's just me being strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.66,0:13:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't found the answers either!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.06,0:14:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I do know what we must do now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.73,0:14:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Baroque Works' scheming is about\Nto cause a meaningless war!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.00,0:14:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must stop it, at all costs!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.57,0:14:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What they're trying to do\Nis throw this land into ruin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.25,0:14:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if it leaves a\Ndark splotch in our history!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I absolutely refuse to let\NCrocodile have his way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.89,0:14:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we should get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp-san! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you kidding? I can't control\Nthe strength welling up in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Liar.\N--Oh, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.53,0:14:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll stop in a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you how gutsy Manly Usopp is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.67,0:14:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never fall to my knees easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.44,0:14:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What's the big idea?!\N--You fell easily.\N--Well, we should get going, Vivi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.31,0:14:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? But what about Luffy-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.45,0:14:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a worrywart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.61,0:14:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He says he's going\Nto kick Crocodile's butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once he has a clear goal,\Nyou can let him do his own thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.55,0:14:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You know that!\N--Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.09,0:15:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My eyes've adjusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.73,0:15:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On closer look,\Nwe're inside a giant dome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.90,0:15:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Built by people, no less.\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are probably\Nancient ruins or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.00,0:15:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.51,0:15:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this. See all the\Npicture-like writing on this wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.41,0:15:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it in a book or something before.\NThese are ancient letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.08,0:15:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about that stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so nice and cool in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.42,0:15:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're right, then what is\Nthis place doing underground?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it built underground, or did\Nit get buried after it was built?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, I get the feeling they\Nwere trying to hide this building...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno who did it,\Nbut they sure worked hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, it's none of my business,\Nand it doesn't interest me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.58,0:16:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What we gotta do now is get the\Nhell outta here. Right, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? But it's cool in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.55,0:16:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No! Let's stay here a\Nlittle longer! It's hot outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.06,0:16:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Time to get outta here!\NWe gotta meet up with the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.30,0:16:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's Zoro's comedy hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.44,0:16:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.81,0:16:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.31,0:16:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it! I missed 'cause\Nthe target's so small!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.59,0:16:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.19,0:16:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again, what are you trying to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.59,0:16:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just grab onto the boulder above the hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.83,0:16:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is getting annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.70,0:16:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.67,0:16:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.26,0:17:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Alright! All better!\N--Are you crazy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.79,0:17:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna grab on to\Nnow that you broke that boulder?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.13,0:17:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay! I got an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.36,0:17:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?!\N--Chopper. You should probably turn little.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.30,0:17:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?\N--Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.20,0:17:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, now I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.61,0:17:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grab on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.77,0:17:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give it up. This is the only way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.74,0:17:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.08,0:17:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.28,0:17:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Spring!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.32,0:17:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.80,0:17:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are we going to land?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.87,0:17:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heck if I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.40,0:17:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mean--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.54,0:18:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to just give it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.11,0:18:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody mentioned this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Successful escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.62,0:18:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I did choose\Nthe wrong ship to ride on...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.87,0:18:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're on the same wavelength today...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking the same thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.64,0:18:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp. You're falling behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to\Nshowing how gutsy you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I only said that out of spirit...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.49,0:18:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there! Just a little further!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.56,0:19:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.60,0:19:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's written all over your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.17,0:19:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I do have faith in them, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.47,0:19:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm guessing you'll never\Nget over being a worrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.28,0:19:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that has its good points, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.55,0:19:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You people are amazing.\N--Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've felt that way ever since Little Garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.35,0:19:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you have so much\Nfaith in your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.26,0:19:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.16,0:19:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something I'm conscious of.\NI've never even thought about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what's amazing.\NHaving unconditional faith in someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not very easy to have.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm. I'm not really sure,\Nbut maybe it's because
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.54,0:19:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we all do what we can\Nas best as we can?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.31,0:19:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A while back, he said\Nsomething on the island I lived on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.78,0:19:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how to\Nuse swords, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.05,0:19:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how to sail the oceans!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.65,0:19:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.86,0:20:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I can't lie, either!\N--Hey, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.12,0:20:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm confident that\NI can't live without help!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.60,0:20:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember those words very well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought,\N"Oh, this is how these pirates are..."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.07,0:20:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alone, there's a limit to your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.87,0:20:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, things you really want\Nto do are too much for one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.18,0:20:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it amounts to nothing if those\Nfriends don't do what they can.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops! Sorry that wasn't an answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Thank you!\N--I can't keep my thoughts\Nstraight in this heat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.56,0:20:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That answered plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.97,0:20:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That may be one of this country's forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.81,0:20:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.87,0:20:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course he gets energetic\Nwhen it starts to cool off...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.48,0:20:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.22,0:21:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind has changed direction.\NI smell something!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.32,0:21:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--No doubt about it! It's Nami's perfume!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.25,0:21:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's this way!\N--Way to go! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.69,0:21:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We found Nami and the others!\NIn the sunset direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.43,0:21:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For reals?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.73,0:21:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.83,0:21:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't rush off on your own!\NWe'll get separated again, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.02,0:21:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm with them,\NI start to see many things...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.36,0:21:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These people may have the answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.08,0:22:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the adventurers\NI dreamed of when I was a child
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.08,0:22:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I continue on to the ends of emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.99,0:22:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I scoop up my hands, and the sand\Nand time that spills from them
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.63,0:22:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,show me that this is what\NI was born to do
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.67,0:22:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's continue swimming\Nat a near-tumbling speed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.82,0:22:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until we wash up someday\Non a white sandy beach
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.46,0:22:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no one knows about
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.45,0:23:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we make it to Yuba?!\NI can't tell with all this sand!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.68,0:23:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The city doesn't look right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.82,0:23:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--This is horrible!\N--Wasn't this an oasis?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.52,0:23:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sand has raised the ground!\NThe oasis has been swallowed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.82,0:23:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there doesn't seem to be any water...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.26,0:23:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rebel army doesn't seem to be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.53,0:23:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will stop the revolt!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.26,0:23:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.63,0:23:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Spiders Caf√© at 8 O'Clock--\NThe Enemy Leaders Gather"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.73,0:23:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.07,0:23:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
